<title>Discovering the IB: What It Is and Why It Matters</title>
  


  <article style="max-width: 800px;margin: auto;background: #fff;padding: 40px;border-radius: 10px">

    
    <p><strong>Fifteen years ago</strong>, <em>aLphabet internationaL schooL</em> opened its doors with one big dream – to enable learners on how to think, not just what to think. Today, as we step boldly into our 16th year, that dream is stronger than ever – thanks to the International Baccalaureate (IB).</p>
    
